"vašeho dotazu a jsou uchovávány po dobu nezbytně nutnou."
msgstr ""
"When you submit the contact form we collect: name, email, phone number "
"(optional) and message content. This data is used solely to answer your "
"inquiry and is retained only as long as necessary."

